body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for reaching out to Star Autosupport. My name is Brian Murphy, how may I assist you today? May I have your name please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello Brian, my name is Frances Bailey.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Frances. Could you kindly provide me with your phone number and address for our records?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my phone number is five five five, two three four, eight nine seven six. And my address is one two three Maple Street, Cityville.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Frances, I've noted down your details. I would also need your email address for communication purposes.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, my email address is Frances dot Bailey at email dot com.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing that information, Frances. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all for now. Thank you for your help.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Frances. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to contact us. Have a great day!
